224
00:10:59,028 --> 00:11:01,758
- Rock the house.
- All right.

225
00:11:01,864 --> 00:11:04,332
<i>George Michael also
didn't know what to do.</i>

226
00:11:04,433 --> 00:11:07,561
<i>If he pointed out that the two
