We can pick her up and surprise her.

244
00:11:59,088 --> 00:12:02,717
You're so right.
This is better than a party for me.

245
00:12:02,825 --> 00:12:05,589
Oh, come on. Grow a pair.

246
00:12:07,530 --> 00:12:11,626
You know, we need some weather balloons for
this party, and maybe a tank of hydrogen.

247
00:12:11,734 --> 00:12:14,601
You know, really float those suckers.

248
00:12:14,704 --> 00:12:16,672
<i>Meanwhile, Michael was
hiding the evidence...</i>

249
00:12:16,772 --> 00:12:19,502
<i>wherever he could
