252
00:12:27,216 --> 00:12:29,707
Damn it.

253
00:12:29,819 --> 00:12:32,344
<i>And the family picked up
Rita in the only vehicle...</i>

254
00:12:32,455 --> 00:12:34,775
<i>- big enough to hold them all.
- Hey, hey. Excuse me. Rita?</i>

255
00:12:34,857 --> 00:12:38,452
- I'm Rita.
- We're here to pick you up for Michael.

256
00:12:38,561 --> 00:12:40,688
Uh, you can just go in the cabin.

257
00:12:44,867 --> 00:12:48,268
- Michael?
- Oh, he's not here.

258
00:12:48,371 --> 00:12:51,738
- We're his family.
- Oh, his family.

259
00:12:51,841 --> 00:12:54,935
- We're nice.
