drugged him and had your way with him.

365
00:18:27,578 --> 00:18:29,432
How is that even possible?

366
00:18:29,445 --> 00:18:31,309
No, George Michael.
We didn't do anything.

367
00:18:31,415 --> 00:18:33,906
I just wanted him to think
we did. Don't you see?

368
00:18:34,018 --> 00:18:36,646
<i>I drugged him not to go
all the way with him.</i>

369
00:18:36,754 --> 00:18:40,315
