374
00:18:51,469 --> 00:18:53,562
because apparently
the retainer is all used up.

375
00:18:53,671 --> 00:18:56,333
He took my call.
He's very good.

376
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,499
Yeah, that's how the retainer
got eaten up, okay?

377
00:18:58,609 --> 00:19:00,649
The secretary took it all
down here on a transcript.

378
00:19:00,678 --> 00:19:03,078
Ugh. She's very good too.

379
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:06,013
<i>- I'm not paying for this.
- Well, what am I supposed to do?</i>

380
00:19:06,117 --> 00:19:08,290
I don't know, Lindsay.
Thing you say on page

