00:19:08,303 --> 00:19:10,486
seven looks like it could
be worth some money.

382
00:19:13,524 --> 00:19:15,856
- Speaking to me yet?
- It's only been an hour.

383
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:18,047
Here's what I don't understand.
What were you

384
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:20,158
guys doing with Rita
in the first place?

385
00:19:20,264 --> 00:19:22,858
We just wanted to do
something nice for you, Michael...

386
00:19:22,967 --> 00:19:25,367
'cause you do so much for us.

387
00:19:25,469 --> 00:19:27,369
I guess we screwed it up.

388
00:19:27,471 --> 00:19:30,372
No, I screwed it up, 'cause
I was trying to impress her.

389
00:19:30,474 --> 00:19:32,840
Let's face it.
She's probably too good for me.

390
00:19:32,943 --> 00:19:36,276
No. What you need to do
is go to her and ask for another chance.

391
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:39,110
She'd be lucky
to have you, Michael.

392
00:19:41,452 --> 00:19:44,216
Thanks, Gob.
Sometimes you do surprise me.

393
00:19:44,321 --> 00:19:46,789
I've got one more surprise for you.

394
00:19:49,126 --> 00:19:51,185
<i>It ain't easy being wh...</i>

395
00:19:51,295 --> 00:19:53,786
<i>And Michael did try again with Rita...</i>

396
00:19:53,898 --> 00:19:56,526
<i>but this time determined
